com.nabto.api

Enum NabtoStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NabtoStatus>
      • com.nabto.api.NabtoStatus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<NabtoStatus>

    public enum NabtoStatus
extends java.lang.Enum<NabtoStatus>
    The NabtoStatus enumeration is the set of status values that most of the functions in the Client API return.
